ğŸ“ SET B â€“ Coding Question 1 (Basic)

â“ Question:

Create a User class and initialize using apply. Print using also.


---

âœ… Answer:

data class User(var name: String = "", var age: Int = 0, var city: String = "")

fun main() {

    val user = User().apply {
        name = "Viney"
        age = 22
        city = "Delhi"
    }

    user.also {
        println(it)
    }
}


