7. Flow cold because â†’ B âœ… Starts when collected


8. putExtra used for â†’ B âœ… Data sharing


9. Implicit Intent uses â†’ B âœ… Action


10. Bound service ends when â†’ B âœ… All unbind


11. Binder used in â†’ B âœ… Bound service


12. AIDL needed for â†’ B âœ… Different process


13. ContentResolver works with â†’ B âœ… ContentProvider


14. JNI calls â†’ B âœ… C/C++


15. .so is â†’ B âœ… Shared object


16. Frida used for â†’ A âœ… Security testing


17. onBind returns â†’ B âœ… IBinder


18. Messenger alternative to â†’ A âœ… AIDL


